`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * cast 'cure poison' <character>

 Just as Garion did with the poisons in his body while in Salmissra's Palace,
some people have the ability to use their Will to remove toxins from the
bloodstream.

